Logical: Option
Title: "Option"
Description: "Option"

* id 1..1 Identifier "Unique ID for option"
* code 0..1 Identifier "Unique CODE for option"
* href 0..1 Identifier "Unique URL where the option is available from"
* name 1..1 string "Name of option"
* shortName 1..1 string "Short name of option"
* description 0..1 string "Description of option"
* attributeValues 0..* AttributeValue "additional attributes that are in this option"